values:
Now THIS picture is absolutely adorable!!! (eventhough I still detect "product" in the hair and I'm having flashbacks to my grandmothers furniture)


That's right girls... I went to the Jr Prom with this stallion.

Please and Thank You.

I moved this weekend...again
I listened to the song "Henry the 8th" 4 times too many..again
I spilled a beer all over the couch when I fell asleep...again
I watched Anne of Green Gables and loved it...again
I ruined my friendship with Brian..again

I need to recover from my "vacation" I fear my heart has deflated and my head might explode. 

I suffer from stupidity and impulsiveness and guilt.
It is NOT a gift.

I have a sinus cold. 
It's STILL summer and I have a COLD.
When I bend over to tie my shoe my head feels so heavy.
I fear the next time it's untied I'll fall rightover.
 
What if I can't get up?
What if I have to sleep on the floor at work because of my HUGE head?!?!
It's low end berber carpet, it can't be all that comfortable.

FUCK!!!!

BTW...I breathed on this LiveJournal you might want to wash your hands.

I got 3D glasses...
The 3rd dimension is AMAZING.
Do u ever feel like this?

So the people I work with are stressed out...neurotic even.  Why?  Who knows. It has become painfully obvious that there are just not enough hours in the day and it really does suck that the summer is our "busy" time...
but seriously, learn to budget your time and pick a couple of days a week to throw down a couple of extra hours.  Don't stress all day, everyday, stay late, get nothing done becuase you're too busy stressing and then spend ADDITIONAL time complaining that you can't get out to enjoy the nice weather!!!  

Get over it, get it done and get outside!!!  

:Gross:

13 days 'till VEGAS fuckers!!!

Seriously, people need to fucking chill!

You're all going to have heart attacks before you're 40.  Life goes on whether or not you stress about it...so why bother. 

CHILL!!!

Now that I'm not contageous I've spent the day doing laundry (sheets, etc), cleaning my house, burning my hands off in wicked hot water washing all the dishes I've touched and lysoling every door knob and/or counter top that I may have accidentally breathed on.  (I even "lysoled" the top of the lysol becuase I touched it yesterday whilst lysoling after myself)  Yeah...I DON'T EVER want this again. It fucking blows.

In other exciting news...I was able to eat mac n'cheese today.  So in addition to cleaning...there's been a lot of mac n'cheese, popcicles, gatorade and Ween. Besides the sick part I'd have to say today was a decent "tori" day.
and it fucking blows.  out of work 'till 23rd Drs orders. that is all.

"...you are not supposed to 'get it.'  If you 'got it' you'd be dead
and that severely limits your allowable social outings per week." 

-B.McCarthy
